🌟Honored to announce my role as Global Ambassador for Ice Open Network (#ION)!

@ice.blockchain is at the forefront of blockchain innovation, bringing the benefits of Web3 to everyone. Their mission to restore control, privacy, and ownership to individuals deeply aligns with my values of respect, independence, and empowerment.

With a community that’s now over 20 million strong, #IceOpenNetwork is creating waves, and I’m eager to inspire others to join us in this journey for change!

